HELP1: O le 'Acrostics Maker' ose meafaigaluega e fesoasoani i le fatuina o se faasologa o upu poʻo se fuaiupu e tauloto ai se upu e faʻaaoga ai ona mataitusi.
HELP10: Fa'amolemole FIAFIA, ma fa'asalalau atu le tala lelei na fesoasoani ai le 'Acrostics Maker' ia te oe e manatua ai igoa fa'apitoa i lou olaga.
HELP2: Mo se fa'ata'ita'iga, ina ia manatua se {spcNm}, ose manu e pei o le racoon e 4 vae mai Madagascar, e mafai ona e fa'aogaina le acrostic lea:
HELP3: O lo'o lisiina upu i koluma i lalo o mata'itusi ta'itasi o le upu acrostic.
HELP4: O lo'o fa'atonuina fa'aalafapeta e fa'auiga filifilia fa'atasi ai ma fa'amaumauga o lomifefiloi o lo'o lisiina i lalo o fa'ailoga ta'itasi mo mata'itusi ta'itasi.
HELP5: E filifilia fa'amaumauga a le lomifefiloi pe a iai le fa'auigaina.
HELP7: Filifili se upu se tasi i koluma taitasi mo mataitusi taitasi
HELP8: Fa'asa'o le upu i luga pe a mana'omia.
HELP9: Kiliki 'Copy Acrostic' ile pito i luga e kopi ai lau acrostic.
